headline: A Look At Franklin Resources (BEN) Valuation After Alternative Credit Merger And Tokenization Push
summary: Franklin Resources (BEN) is back in focus after Franklin Templeton combined its U.S. and European alternative credit arms under the Benefit Street Partners brand, while also pushing ahead with tokenization efforts in existing fund products.
